operation modes
---

16 bit  => real mode
32 bits => protected mode
64 bits => 64-bit submode

registers
---

{A,B,C,D..}X  => 16 bit
E{A,B,C,D..}X => 32 bit
R{A,B,C,D..}X => 64 bit

sizes
---

byte  => 01
word  => 02
dword => 04
qword => 08
tword => 10
oword => 16
yword => 32
zword => 64

sections
---

.data => initialized variables
.text => code
.bss => uninitialized variables
.rodata | .rdata => readonly data (e.g: constants)

